                <div class="content">
                	<h2><span class="red bold lines">E</span><span class="red bold">xpanding Across Borders, </span>A Global Voice</h2>
                    <p>With global brands and wide-reaching content, it’s no surprise our audience has an international profile. That’s why, through a combination of owned & operated properties and local partners, we’ve expanded our leading vertical brands specializing in technology, gaming and men’s lifestyle to better serve local audiences while leveraging our core content produced in the USA, UK, Canada and Australia. Today, we have 28 international editions across our three major platforms -- IGN, PCMag and AskMen. Visit <a href="http://world.ziffdavis.com" class="reg" target="_blank">world.ziffdavis.com</a> for more information.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
